name: VisionTek SoundTube Pro V2 - Speaker - for portable use - wireless - NFC, Bluetooth | Dell USA
description: With the VisionTek SoundTube Pro V2, you can listen to your music anywhere you go. Enjoy high-quality sound with rich bass and clear treble. The waterproof IPX7 build makes this an ideal portable speaker to take on the go to the beach or back rails. With TWS technology, you can connect two SountTube Pro V2 speakers for a true stereo experience.
